    <p>• For­mer US Open cham­pi­ons Andy Mur­ray and Kim Cli­jsters were both handed wild cards on Thursday for the hard-court Grand Slam which will start on Aug 31.</p>
    <p>For­mer world No. 1 Mur­ray is ranked 129th af­ter a lengthy bat­tle with a hip in­jury, while Cli­jsters re­turned ear­lier this year af­ter re­tir­ing in 2012.</p>


